headline: HPE Lands on Evercore’s Tactical Outperform List With $28 Target
summary: Hewlett-Packard Enterprise Company (NYSE:HPE) is one of the Trending AI Stocks on Wall Street. On November 10, Evercore ISI maintained its Outperform rating on the stock with a $28 price target. The firm has also added HPE to its Tactical Outperform List, anticipating robust Jan-quarter guide, Juniper synergies, and AI compute margin lift to drive continued […]
